WEBVTT

00:09.960 --> 00:10.800
It's a clever plan,

00:11.400 --> 00:13.560
but it doesn't seem
like your usual approach.

00:14.320 --> 00:15.440
Which advisor gave you this idea?

00:16.280 --> 00:17.280
Spill it.

00:18.960 --> 00:20.280
It was

00:21.120 --> 00:22.000
a female advisor.

00:22.760 --> 00:24.840
A woman? Who?

00:25.360 --> 00:26.640
Who?

00:30.440 --> 00:31.760
You won't tell me?

00:31.840 --> 00:32.840
So mysterious.

00:33.360 --> 00:35.040
Don't tell me it's your sweetheart.

00:35.120 --> 00:36.240
Nonsense.

00:44.240 --> 00:46.600
Come on, just tell me
which family she's from.

00:46.680 --> 00:48.840
I will pull out all the stops
to arrange a match for you.

00:50.000 --> 00:51.600
Stop joking around.

00:51.680 --> 00:52.880
My mother is still unwell.

00:52.960 --> 00:54.840
Don't go spouting nonsense to her.

00:56.520 --> 00:57.360
Still, if you ask me,

00:57.960 --> 01:00.000
aren't you overthinking this case?

01:01.040 --> 01:02.280
Hearing that your mother is ill,

01:02.960 --> 01:04.720
His and Her majesties have sent
court physicians several times

01:05.440 --> 01:06.600
to check on her.

01:07.200 --> 01:08.480
They seem as concerned as ever.

01:09.000 --> 01:10.800
And with Grand Secretary Wu
mediating in court,

01:11.320 --> 01:14.360
I'd say His Majesty
will at most issue a mild reprimand.

01:14.440 --> 01:15.520
Nothing serious will happen
to the Duke of Ding.

01:19.000 --> 01:20.000
Let's hope not.

02:41.720 --> 02:45.160
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

02:54.200 --> 02:56.120
Grand Secretary, Grand Secretary!

02:58.000 --> 03:00.040
What I said before His Majesty
wasn't directed at you.

03:00.640 --> 03:03.840
I had to answer
His Majesty's question impartially.

03:06.160 --> 03:07.760
Impartially…

03:08.280 --> 03:10.120
If it's for the sake
of stabilizing the court,

03:10.200 --> 03:11.040
you did right.

03:11.880 --> 03:14.480
But this matter concerns
major issues in the southeast.

03:15.160 --> 03:17.840
It has nothing to do with
the Ministry of Rites, right?

03:20.520 --> 03:21.720
It's the time of the Dragon Boat Festival.

03:22.480 --> 03:27.840
Minister Dou, why don't you
take a few days off to rest at home?

03:31.280 --> 03:32.440
Since you've said so,

03:32.520 --> 03:33.920
I'll follow your instruction.

03:51.240 --> 03:52.240
Grand Secretary Wu.

03:53.400 --> 03:56.200
Is Minister Dou from the western
Dou family of the capital?

03:56.280 --> 03:57.280
Yes.

03:58.160 --> 04:00.080
After reading the officials'
impeachment memorials,

04:00.160 --> 04:02.560
His Majesty inquired
about Mei Sun's health.

04:03.280 --> 04:05.360
His Majesty was clearly
concerned about him.

04:05.440 --> 04:07.320
But Dou Shi Shu claimed that

04:07.400 --> 04:09.400
The Duke of Ding's detention
and return to the capital

04:09.480 --> 04:11.160
could destabilize
the southeastern regions.

04:11.880 --> 04:13.560
Isn't that just a veiled way

04:13.640 --> 04:15.920
of accusing Mei Sun of
amassing troops and risking rebellion?

04:18.240 --> 04:20.279
Does he have a grudge against my uncle?

04:20.360 --> 04:22.440
Before his promotion
to the Ministry of Rites,

04:22.520 --> 04:25.040
he was a cautious and low-profile official

04:25.120 --> 04:27.560
who never overstepped.

04:28.480 --> 04:30.560
Turns out, he was simply biding his time,

04:30.640 --> 04:33.600
eyeing a seat in
the Grand Secretariat all along.

04:34.280 --> 04:35.880
If my uncle is painted as a traitor,

04:36.440 --> 04:38.360
then he, as the one
who speaks out against him,

04:38.440 --> 04:39.840
would earn credit
for rooting out treachery.

04:40.360 --> 04:42.240
Take good care of your mother.

04:42.320 --> 04:43.760
When Mei Sun returns to the capital,

04:43.840 --> 04:45.400
the Grand Secretariat
will figure out a solution.

04:47.120 --> 04:48.440
Thank you, Grand Secretary Wu.

04:53.720 --> 04:55.640
Have you ever tried
the Dou family's rice dumplings?

04:56.720 --> 04:57.920
Rice dumplings?

04:58.000 --> 04:59.280
You should try some.

05:05.040 --> 05:08.920
Young Lady Zhao must've
tipped off her uncle then.

05:09.440 --> 05:10.760
What a scheming woman!

05:11.320 --> 05:13.040
Didn't you praise her for being sharp,

05:13.120 --> 05:14.360
righteous, and loyal before?

05:15.640 --> 05:18.000
I… I've never been good at judging people.

05:19.680 --> 05:21.520
If she were really plotting against Uncle,

05:21.600 --> 05:24.040
Jiying Guards would have
already stormed Tan Manor.

05:24.120 --> 05:25.480
Yet everything there is peaceful,

05:25.560 --> 05:27.160
the child is well cared for.

05:27.240 --> 05:29.720
Plus, General Yan is keeping
an eye on her.

05:31.200 --> 05:32.720
That makes it even stranger.

05:32.800 --> 05:34.880
She has been living
in seclusion in the countryside.

05:34.960 --> 05:36.600
How does she know so much
about court affairs?

05:38.200 --> 05:39.280
There's another possibility.

05:39.960 --> 05:40.920
It's not just Dou Shi Shu,

05:41.520 --> 05:43.920
perhaps the entire Dou family is her pawn.

05:44.520 --> 05:46.360
She can orchestrate moves from afar,
manipulating people.

05:47.520 --> 05:49.680
The young lord could be using
her leverage against us.

05:51.360 --> 05:52.880
If that's true,

05:52.960 --> 05:53.840
it's hard to imagine

05:53.920 --> 05:55.880
that someone as beautiful
as Young Lady Zhao

05:55.960 --> 05:57.240
would be so cruelly calculating.

06:00.160 --> 06:01.480
Uncle hasn't reached the capital.

06:01.560 --> 06:04.040
And we've already clashed
with the Dou family twice.

06:04.120 --> 06:07.240
There will undoubtedly be more to come.

06:08.480 --> 06:11.600
We must uncover their true intentions.

06:17.200 --> 06:19.360
Xing Yi has long

06:19.880 --> 06:21.760
suffered from rheumatism,

06:22.720 --> 06:25.240
so I sent him some mugwort oil for relief.

06:26.080 --> 06:27.720
It wasn't anything valuable,

06:28.560 --> 06:29.840
yet he still returned it.

06:31.000 --> 06:32.400
We're in-laws

06:32.920 --> 06:34.360
and colleagues in court,

06:35.040 --> 06:38.080
but the way he avoids any connection,
it's as if we're complete strangers.

06:40.480 --> 06:43.160
My father fears give
others cause to fault him,

06:43.240 --> 06:44.520
lest it implicates our family.

06:45.120 --> 06:46.360
Despite your busy official duties,

06:46.440 --> 06:47.600
you still keep my father's health

06:47.680 --> 06:50.040
in mind while you're home on break,

06:50.120 --> 06:51.400
I must thank you for that.

06:51.480 --> 06:52.320
No need for thanks.

06:53.240 --> 06:54.240
We're family, after all.

06:55.040 --> 06:56.360
While I'm home on leave,

06:56.440 --> 06:57.800
there's actually something

06:57.880 --> 06:59.800
I'd like to discuss with you and Shi Ying.

06:59.880 --> 07:00.880
Have a seat.

07:01.640 --> 07:03.720
Shou Gu is 23 this year,

07:04.440 --> 07:06.880
and Ming is 16, aren't they?

07:06.960 --> 07:08.080
Yes.

07:08.920 --> 07:10.480
If there were a son in the family,

07:10.560 --> 07:11.960
he'd be preparing
for the imperial exams now.

07:12.040 --> 07:14.240
I've failed to provide
an heir for the Dou family

07:14.320 --> 07:17.120
and have burdened you
with concerns for the family's future.

07:17.200 --> 07:18.520
It's my fault.

07:20.720 --> 07:23.920
You've been managing the entire household.

07:24.000 --> 07:24.840
How could it be your fault?

07:25.560 --> 07:26.920
If anyone's to blame, it's Shi Ying.

07:27.000 --> 07:28.600
Even as an official,

07:28.680 --> 07:30.480
his heart is still set on academia.

07:31.120 --> 07:33.480
He has no grasp of court dynamics
or political affairs.

07:33.560 --> 07:35.760
If our family wants to secure our footing,

07:37.240 --> 07:39.000
we can't rely on just one family.

07:39.080 --> 07:42.760
If Ming marries Young Master Wu,

07:43.280 --> 07:46.840
our families will become one,
united in purpose.

07:46.920 --> 07:49.200
The children actually
have a lot in common.

07:49.280 --> 07:51.160
They're just a little shy
around each other.

07:52.040 --> 07:55.120
In the case, invite De Zhen to
our Dragon Boat Festival banquet.

07:55.640 --> 07:57.560
As elders, it's our duty
to give them a nudge.

07:57.640 --> 07:59.760
All right, I'll send the invitation.

07:59.840 --> 08:03.040
Also, the Marquis of Jining has finished

08:03.120 --> 08:04.280
his three-year mourning period.

08:04.360 --> 08:07.640
It's time to address
his informal engagement with Shou Gu.

08:07.720 --> 08:09.760
Include him in the invitation
and see where it leads.

08:10.360 --> 08:12.160
I'll speak to Shi Ying about it.

08:12.760 --> 08:13.640
Understood.

08:14.320 --> 08:17.560
It'd be great if Young Lady Ming
marries Young Master Wu,

08:18.080 --> 08:21.200
but wasn't Dou Zhao's childhood
engagement already called off?

08:21.280 --> 08:24.640
Why is Fifth Master
suddenly so invested in it again?

08:25.280 --> 08:27.200
He's not on leave for rest.

08:27.280 --> 08:29.080
My father already sent word.

08:29.680 --> 08:31.680
Shi Shu misspoke in court

08:31.760 --> 08:33.080
and offended Grand Secretary Wu.

08:33.159 --> 08:35.280
He was forced to take leave.

08:36.280 --> 08:39.320
He's now pinning his hopes on
the marriages of his two nieces,

08:39.400 --> 08:41.880
one to secure a powerful alliance

08:41.960 --> 08:44.280
and the other to appease an influential
but declining noble family.

08:44.360 --> 08:47.680
But isn't the connection
with your family enough?

08:48.480 --> 08:50.400
My father is too principled

08:50.480 --> 08:52.200
and has never favored family over reason.

08:52.800 --> 08:54.720
Now that he's aiming to
join the Grand Secretariat.

08:54.800 --> 08:57.360
Father won't involve himself in this mess.

08:58.160 --> 09:01.040
But if Dou Zhao really
becomes Marchioness of Jining,

09:01.120 --> 09:03.360
wouldn't that put her above you?

09:05.080 --> 09:07.880
Wei Ting Yu is notorious
for his extravagant and frivolous ways.

09:08.400 --> 09:10.880
Though their family has held the title
for generations and appears respectable,

09:10.960 --> 09:13.160
they've burned through
their wealth in recent years,

09:13.240 --> 09:14.920
especially with lavish funerals.

09:16.000 --> 09:17.520
His sister, Wei Ting Zhen,

09:17.600 --> 09:19.360
married the Duke of Jing as a second wife.

09:20.520 --> 09:23.640
That entire family is opportunistic.

09:23.720 --> 09:25.880
There's potential to work together
if the terms are right.

09:29.200 --> 09:30.160
Madam, be careful!

09:31.040 --> 09:33.560
These butterflies are drawn
to those cursed albizia flowers.

09:34.480 --> 09:36.440
If their wing scales land on your skin,

09:36.520 --> 09:37.600
it'll cause unbearable itching.

09:38.360 --> 09:41.080
I'll have the servants catch them
all right away.

09:43.200 --> 09:47.120
They're so beautiful.
It'd be a shame to get rid of them all.

10:13.560 --> 10:15.400
Have a drink, My Lord.

10:24.880 --> 10:26.040
The painting looks great.

10:26.120 --> 10:28.320
-What a beautiful painting.
-Thank you.

10:28.400 --> 10:29.280
You're such a great painter, My Lord.

10:39.360 --> 10:41.000
Duchess of Jing,

10:41.080 --> 10:43.480
what a pleasant surprise!
We weren't prepared to greet you.

10:44.560 --> 10:45.560
Where is His Lordship?

10:46.080 --> 10:47.440
His Lordship…

10:50.280 --> 10:51.800
My Lady, My Lady…

10:51.880 --> 10:53.040
Excuse me.

10:53.640 --> 10:56.160
My Lady, please slow down.
Please watch your step.

10:56.760 --> 10:59.520
Please allow me
to inform His Lordship first.

11:01.760 --> 11:04.400
My Lady, please show mercy!

11:04.480 --> 11:07.680
If you barge in, His Lordship will
surely punish me severely!

11:09.560 --> 11:11.400
Then let me save him
the trouble and kill you now!

11:12.680 --> 11:13.680
My Lady…

11:16.000 --> 11:17.600
-Interesting.
-So beautiful.

11:19.080 --> 11:19.960
Pei Jin.

11:23.040 --> 11:23.880
Ting Zhen?

11:29.560 --> 11:31.120
Young Lady Dou Zhao?

11:31.200 --> 11:32.640
Why are we talking about her again?

11:32.720 --> 11:35.880
I've heard from reliable sources
that she's made

11:35.960 --> 11:36.840
DUCHESS OF JING, WEI TING ZHEN

11:36.920 --> 11:38.600
at least this much in Futing.

11:40.040 --> 11:41.720
Whatever the amount,
it's just worldly possessions.

11:42.240 --> 11:44.160
Didn't Master Shi Ying send us a letter,

11:44.240 --> 11:46.640
saying that matters of marriage
should follow fate?

11:46.720 --> 11:47.720
Isn't that essentially saying
to forget about it?

11:47.800 --> 11:49.440
Not at all.

11:49.520 --> 11:51.160
The Dou family just sent an invitation

11:51.240 --> 11:53.080
to join their Dragon Boat Festival outing.

11:55.400 --> 11:57.600
These past few years,
with disasters everywhere,

11:57.680 --> 11:59.440
our harvest income has been halved,

11:59.520 --> 12:00.800
yet our household expenses
haven't decreased.

12:01.560 --> 12:02.880
Without some external support,

12:03.400 --> 12:04.960
do you know how much it costs

12:05.040 --> 12:06.760
to keep this estate running?

12:07.360 --> 12:08.200
-I…
-Listen to me.

12:08.800 --> 12:10.320
Once Father's mourning period is over,

12:10.400 --> 12:11.600
finalize the engagement quickly.

12:12.200 --> 12:14.720
Ting Zhen, the Dou family
is full of strife,

12:15.480 --> 12:16.720
and she grew up in the countryside.

12:16.800 --> 12:19.360
Some young gentlemen who
attended a Dou family banquet said

12:19.880 --> 12:21.800
she doesn't observe propriety
between men and women,

12:21.880 --> 12:23.920
speaks rudely,
and even contradicts her elders.

12:24.000 --> 12:25.240
She's completely uncouth!

12:27.440 --> 12:28.640
I was just about to tell you

12:28.720 --> 12:30.240
that Dou Zhao is famously beautiful,

12:30.840 --> 12:32.920
a true flower among women.

12:33.000 --> 12:35.120
I thought she might catch your eye.

12:36.880 --> 12:39.120
But since you despise her so much,

12:39.720 --> 12:40.960
I suppose I should just drop this matter.

12:46.280 --> 12:48.960
Three, two…

12:49.560 --> 12:50.560
Ting Zhen.

12:54.160 --> 12:56.120
I am a marquis, after all.

12:56.200 --> 12:58.640
I should be more magnanimous.

12:59.320 --> 13:00.800
Since we've accepted the invitation,

13:00.880 --> 13:03.800
not attending would be discourteous.

13:03.880 --> 13:06.120
I'll follow whatever you decide.

13:12.160 --> 13:13.600
What a shame.

13:14.320 --> 13:15.600
One wrong stroke,

13:15.680 --> 13:17.320
and this Plum Blossom painting is ruined.

13:17.920 --> 13:18.920
It's not ruined.

13:20.720 --> 13:23.720
-It was such a beautiful painting!
-Don't worry.

13:31.320 --> 13:32.800
Come, take a look.

13:32.880 --> 13:34.720
Who would have thought
That late in the winter snow

13:34.800 --> 13:37.200
A single plum blossom would
Emerge beyond the wall?

13:37.280 --> 13:38.760
Brilliant, truly brilliant!

13:40.000 --> 13:41.000
Indeed!

13:45.560 --> 13:47.360
It's not like tiger amulets
are hard to find.

13:47.440 --> 13:48.880
Wang Ying Xue just had to force
you and Dou Ming to make one.

13:49.480 --> 13:51.480
She's just trying
to torture your poor fingers.

13:51.560 --> 13:55.880
Yes, that's why I'm making my stitching
crooked and messy.

13:56.440 --> 13:58.840
The goal is to let Dou Ming
outshine me, after all.

13:58.920 --> 14:00.000
So that you can hide your talent?

14:00.600 --> 14:02.000
Not entirely.

14:02.800 --> 14:05.720
The real headache is Wang Ying Xue
making you organize the banquet.

14:06.320 --> 14:09.160
Old Madam and Master Shi Ying only
just started to mend their relationship.

14:09.240 --> 14:11.200
With all these people
gathering for the festival,

14:11.280 --> 14:13.040
I'm worried it'll cause
more misunderstandings.

14:13.120 --> 14:16.280
I think Wang Ying Xue is just
using the festival as an excuse

14:16.360 --> 14:18.200
to play matchmaker between
you girls and the young men.

14:21.960 --> 14:23.120
Young Lady,

14:23.200 --> 14:25.000
we've received a letter
from Zhaowen Bookstore.

14:43.360 --> 14:46.800
Wu Shan has been appointed
into the Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

14:46.880 --> 14:49.240
It's one thing for Wu Shan to come.

14:49.320 --> 14:50.360
But after six years,

14:50.440 --> 14:52.120
does Wei Ting Yu not get the hint?

14:52.720 --> 14:54.800
And now he's coming too? Shameless.

14:54.880 --> 14:55.880
Exactly.

14:56.960 --> 14:59.360
The doctor said she doesn't
have much time left.

14:59.440 --> 15:01.200
Once she's gone, I'll marry you.

15:04.440 --> 15:06.400
Song Mo has grown
arrogant with his merits.

15:07.000 --> 15:10.640
He seduced the Marchioness of Jining,
Dou Zhao, and ran off with her.

15:10.720 --> 15:13.040
They shall be executed
to set things right.

15:14.200 --> 15:15.800
This matter needs
to be settled sooner or later.

15:16.720 --> 15:17.760
If he dares to come,

15:18.560 --> 15:20.520
I'll make sure to give him
a proper welcome.

15:27.720 --> 15:28.720
Please.

15:31.000 --> 15:32.680
Such beautiful scenery,
and the renovations are impressive.

15:33.280 --> 15:35.120
As expected of Madam Cui,

15:35.640 --> 15:37.960
this estate exudes
such elegance and refinement.

15:39.080 --> 15:42.520
My mother-in-law doesn't
enjoy the noise of the city,

15:42.600 --> 15:44.920
-so she's been resting here.
-Here.

15:45.000 --> 15:48.160
Over the years, we've been
fortunate to have Zhao take care of her

15:48.240 --> 15:49.800
and manage the estate.

15:49.880 --> 15:51.760
Right now, Zhao is probably tending

15:51.840 --> 15:54.200
to her grandmother's afternoon rest,

15:54.280 --> 15:56.200
so she couldn't greet you personally.

15:56.280 --> 15:57.520
Please forgive her.

15:57.600 --> 16:01.360
Zhao is gentle, virtuous,
and skilled in managing the household.

16:01.440 --> 16:04.120
Everyone who meets her
has nothing but praise.

16:04.200 --> 16:06.400
Even her sisters

16:06.480 --> 16:08.080
are graceful, poised,

16:08.160 --> 16:10.400
and exceptionally intelligent.

16:19.240 --> 16:22.200
-Uncle.
-Ru? What are you…

16:22.280 --> 16:23.560
Let me catch a few more chickens

16:23.640 --> 16:24.920
to add to tonight's dinner.

16:25.000 --> 16:26.320
Let's go!

16:28.440 --> 16:29.560
I…

16:30.520 --> 16:31.480
Sorry you had to see that.

16:31.560 --> 16:34.560
Zhang Ru takes after her father.

16:34.640 --> 16:35.720
She's livelier than most.

16:36.240 --> 16:39.560
-Come this way, please.
-After you, Young Master Wu.

16:40.320 --> 16:43.480
Aside from Zhang Ru being a little lively,

16:43.560 --> 16:46.440
the other girls are
very demure and composed.

16:46.520 --> 16:49.040
Yes! You lost again!

16:49.120 --> 16:50.600
Put one on your face.

16:51.120 --> 16:52.360
A bet's a bet now. Hurry up!

16:53.280 --> 16:54.360
Whose servant girl is that?

16:54.440 --> 16:56.200
Such uncivilized behavior.
Kick her out now.

16:56.280 --> 16:58.360
-Master Shi Shu!
-Let's play for another round.

16:59.320 --> 17:01.000
It's me, An Su!

17:01.080 --> 17:02.240
An Su?

17:02.320 --> 17:03.960
Zhao taught us this game.

17:04.040 --> 17:05.200
It's so fun!

17:05.280 --> 17:07.240
Why don't you all join us?

17:08.480 --> 17:11.440
Young Lady An Su is skilled
with the abacus,

17:11.520 --> 17:13.119
so it's natural she enjoys such games.

17:13.200 --> 17:15.000
Let's head to the back garden instead.

17:15.079 --> 17:16.160
Follow me.

17:18.560 --> 17:20.839
-Another round. Your turn.
-Come on!

17:20.920 --> 17:22.720
This courtyard

17:22.800 --> 17:26.400
is my mother-in-law's favorite spot.

17:27.000 --> 17:28.079
Look at these flowers and plants,

17:28.160 --> 17:31.280
they're all meticulously cared for.

17:34.720 --> 17:36.800
This place stays green all year round,

17:36.880 --> 17:38.240
full of birdsong and floral scents.

17:38.320 --> 17:40.480
It's lovely.
There's more to see over there.

17:40.560 --> 17:42.000
Let's take a look.

17:42.080 --> 17:43.120
All right.

17:54.000 --> 17:55.200
Ming.

18:09.720 --> 18:12.440
Zhao is a quiet and refined girl.

18:12.520 --> 18:15.360
She usually spends
her time reading and writing.

18:15.440 --> 18:18.280
She's a well-mannered
and graceful young lady.

18:21.000 --> 18:22.040
Come on.

18:22.680 --> 18:24.120
Shou Gu?

18:24.200 --> 18:25.400
That was so rude.

18:25.480 --> 18:28.600
I was trying to welcome our guests
with an archery game,

18:29.280 --> 18:31.880
but it seems my skills are lacking.

18:32.400 --> 18:34.680
I didn't mean to frighten
our esteemed visitors.

18:45.360 --> 18:47.080
It's just as well that the masters

18:47.160 --> 18:49.280
are in the study
discussing official matters.

18:49.360 --> 18:50.880
With those two scholars away,

18:50.960 --> 18:53.480
the children can enjoy
themselves more freely.

18:54.280 --> 18:57.000
I've heard that the Dou family
has two women

18:57.080 --> 18:58.160
renowned for their business acumen,

18:58.240 --> 19:00.280
your esteemed self and Young Lady Zhao.

19:00.360 --> 19:01.440
Madam Wang,

19:01.520 --> 19:04.280
you've helped many officials
accumulate wealth, haven't you?

19:04.880 --> 19:08.400
With a wife like you, Master Shi Ying's
official career is sure to thrive.

19:09.480 --> 19:11.000
You're too kind.

19:11.080 --> 19:13.440
I merely earn a modest profit
to help support the household.

19:14.440 --> 19:17.240
Zhao, on the other hand,
is the real talent.

19:17.320 --> 19:19.120
She already has a substantial fortune

19:19.200 --> 19:21.280
and is incredibly skilled in investments.

19:21.360 --> 19:23.440
She's practically a tycoon.

19:25.400 --> 19:28.480
It's just a pity she doesn't trust me.

19:29.400 --> 19:31.720
If she entrusted some of it to me,

19:31.800 --> 19:35.120
I'd guarantee a 30% profit
in just six months.

19:36.560 --> 19:39.400
Madam, if you can make
this marriage happen,

19:39.480 --> 19:43.720
I'm prepared to invest 40%…

19:44.320 --> 19:47.840
No, 50% of her dowry for you to manage.

19:49.560 --> 19:51.640
You're too generous, My Lady.

19:51.720 --> 19:54.080
If fate blesses us with this union,

19:54.160 --> 19:56.280
why speak of favors at all?
We'd be family.

19:56.360 --> 19:57.400
There's no need for such formalities.

19:58.080 --> 19:59.680
Please enjoy, My Lady.

19:59.760 --> 20:00.640
All right.

20:02.280 --> 20:04.920
What's so entertaining
about archery anyway?

20:05.520 --> 20:07.360
That's precisely why I chose it,
knowing your archery skills are terrible

20:07.440 --> 20:08.920
and that you're vain.

20:09.000 --> 20:12.760
The fun lies in making you think
our interests are completely different,

20:12.840 --> 20:15.360
pushing you to break off the engagement
in a fit of embarrassment.

20:15.440 --> 20:16.800
What are those?

20:17.480 --> 20:19.040
It's a small token from my sister,

20:19.120 --> 20:20.720
kites that soar through the sky,

20:20.800 --> 20:22.800
symbolizing good fortune and success.

20:22.880 --> 20:24.440
To see a thousand miles further,

20:24.520 --> 20:26.320
ascend another story higher.

20:26.920 --> 20:27.960
How thoughtful of Lady Wei.

20:28.480 --> 20:29.960
That's meant for
Master Shi Shu and Master Shi Ying.

20:35.280 --> 20:36.680
Look, Madam.

20:37.200 --> 20:39.120
From this call, greatness begins;

20:39.200 --> 20:41.040
together, gaze at the clouds above.

20:41.120 --> 20:42.680
Such beautiful words!

20:42.760 --> 20:43.840
The meaning is equally wonderful.

20:43.920 --> 20:46.400
I had Pei Jin personally write it,

20:46.480 --> 20:48.800
hoping that after his marriage,
his career will flourish,

20:49.400 --> 20:51.520
and he and Young Lady Zhao
will live in harmony and happiness,

20:51.600 --> 20:53.040
reaching great heights together.

20:55.760 --> 20:57.480
How did you end up shooting
the arrow into the sky?

20:58.520 --> 21:01.600
Young Lady Zhao, are you shooting
at the willows or aiming for the kite?

21:01.680 --> 21:03.560
My archery skills aren't great,

21:03.640 --> 21:04.560
and with today's strong wind,

21:04.640 --> 21:07.120
the arrow accidentally veered off course.

21:09.000 --> 21:10.760
As if I'd ever reach new heights with you.

21:16.520 --> 21:17.640
I'm going to shoot it down.

21:19.840 --> 21:22.200
My Lady, Zhao doesn't
usually practice archery.

21:22.280 --> 21:24.640
I've no idea what's gotten into her today.

21:24.720 --> 21:25.640
Ming,

21:25.720 --> 21:27.480
it's fine for the gentlemen
to indulge in it,

21:27.560 --> 21:29.000
but what are you doing joining in?

21:29.600 --> 21:31.760
Riding and archery are
never meant for young ladies.

21:34.680 --> 21:38.000
My Lady, why don't we head inside
for some fruit and a little rest?

21:38.920 --> 21:39.920
All right.

21:54.680 --> 21:55.520
You…

21:57.200 --> 21:58.160
It's true the wind is quite strong today.

22:00.320 --> 22:03.000
Young Lady Zhao, I hope
I didn't put you in any trouble.

22:03.600 --> 22:05.240
It's just a kite.

22:05.880 --> 22:07.480
Surely His Lordship wouldn't mind that.

22:08.240 --> 22:09.320
Right, My Lord?

22:13.520 --> 22:14.640
Zhao,

22:15.240 --> 22:17.640
could you teach me how to shoot an arrow?

22:19.080 --> 22:22.960
I've heard the Marquis of Jining is
a renowned marksman in the capital.

22:28.280 --> 22:29.240
I…

22:29.800 --> 22:30.720
My Lord.

22:32.200 --> 22:34.640
I wouldn't call myself a marksman,

22:35.440 --> 22:37.320
but a little shooting game like this

22:37.960 --> 22:39.120
is no challenge.

22:43.120 --> 22:44.440
Young Lady Ming, you see,

22:45.040 --> 22:46.360
to shoot accurately and steadily,

22:46.960 --> 22:49.880
the arrowhead needs to be
exactly three times its length,

22:49.960 --> 22:51.600
and the shaft must be
perfectly symmetrical

22:51.680 --> 22:52.960
on all four sides.

22:53.760 --> 22:55.120
Only then can it achieve
what the Zhou rites describe as

22:55.200 --> 22:59.640
"undaunted even by a fierce wind."

23:01.000 --> 23:02.000
You're so knowledgeable.

23:02.080 --> 23:03.320
Knowledgeable indeed.

23:03.400 --> 23:05.400
But if you don't release your arrow soon,

23:06.000 --> 23:07.400
the flowers inside that gourd
will start to wilt.

23:10.160 --> 23:11.640
Now watch closely, Young Lady Ming.

23:14.840 --> 23:16.960
Steady your arm, calm your mind,

23:18.040 --> 23:20.160
and aim for the fullest part of the gourd.

23:25.200 --> 23:26.440
Then, release it…

23:40.640 --> 23:43.720
I… I guess the wind
really is strong today.

23:45.040 --> 23:46.000
So strong.

23:47.600 --> 23:49.320
How about trying another shot, My Lord?

23:52.360 --> 23:54.840
The wind was definitely a factor earlier.

23:55.800 --> 23:56.640
Let me take another shot.

24:00.520 --> 24:02.720
Aim for the gourd's fullest part,

24:02.800 --> 24:04.040
and release.

24:09.480 --> 24:11.640
These arrow fletchings
must not be eagle feathers.

24:11.720 --> 24:12.800
There's no way I'd miss otherwise.

24:12.880 --> 24:16.240
Steady your arm, calm your mind,

24:16.960 --> 24:18.440
and aim for the fullest part of the gourd.

24:23.760 --> 24:26.040
-You got it!
-You really have remarkable insights.

24:26.720 --> 24:28.680
Following your advice,
I figured out how to do it

24:28.760 --> 24:30.040
and hit the target on my first try.

24:31.040 --> 24:32.920
You picked it up rather quickly.

24:34.040 --> 24:35.280
No one learns that fast.

24:35.360 --> 24:36.720
You knew how to shoot, didn't you?

24:41.200 --> 24:42.360
This girl may be attractive,

24:42.440 --> 24:44.200
but she's crude and mean.

24:44.280 --> 24:46.040
Why does she have
to be so infatuated with me?

24:46.120 --> 24:47.440
No, this won't do.

24:47.520 --> 24:48.840
But how do I break off the engagement?

24:48.920 --> 24:50.440
How do I even
bring this up with Ting Zhen?

24:50.520 --> 24:51.800
Such a headache…

24:54.280 --> 24:56.120
Madam Wang's remarks
are too narrow-minded.

24:56.840 --> 24:58.720
In the past, there was Fu Hao,
who expanded territory,

24:58.800 --> 25:00.560
and Mulan, who took her
father's place in the army.

25:01.080 --> 25:03.000
Even in recent times, there's Madam Wa,
who quelled rebellions

25:03.080 --> 25:04.440
and governed a province.

25:04.520 --> 25:07.160
There's no such thing in
the world that men can learn

25:07.240 --> 25:08.720
but women cannot.

25:09.360 --> 25:11.200
She says plenty of nonsense.

25:11.840 --> 25:13.480
I never take any of it to heart.

25:18.520 --> 25:20.640
Mother will blame me
for being useless again.

25:21.560 --> 25:23.560
I've often heard the ladies in the capital

25:24.680 --> 25:27.920
praise your skill in music, chess,
calligraphy, painting, and needlework.

25:28.440 --> 25:30.600
Seeing you today,
you are indeed gentle and poised.

25:31.720 --> 25:33.280
Women are traditionally
valued for their gentleness.

25:33.360 --> 25:36.120
There's no need to belittle yourself.

25:37.120 --> 25:38.600
To Mother,

25:39.840 --> 25:43.000
anything my sister excels at that I cannot

25:43.520 --> 25:44.560
makes me useless.

25:46.200 --> 25:47.120
That's too narrow a perspective.

25:47.920 --> 25:50.400
It's like comparing this branch
of mulberry wood to this arrow.

25:50.920 --> 25:52.280
Which is useful?

25:52.880 --> 25:54.160
Which is useless?

25:55.160 --> 25:57.600
An arrow can be used
in battle to kill enemies.

25:58.360 --> 26:02.160
What use is a tree branch?

26:03.400 --> 26:05.400
A branch, if still on the tree,

26:05.480 --> 26:06.800
can provide shelter from the rain.

26:06.880 --> 26:09.880
Its bark can be made into
paper for people to write on.

26:10.800 --> 26:12.880
The difference lies only in purpose,

26:12.960 --> 26:14.360
not value.

26:15.200 --> 26:16.480
People are the same.

26:32.360 --> 26:33.360
A leaf.

26:45.320 --> 26:47.240
Wearing tiger amulets during the festival

26:47.320 --> 26:48.920
wards off evil and brings good fortune.

26:49.000 --> 26:51.360
The girls personally
embroidered these tiger amulets

26:51.440 --> 26:52.920
for you gentlemen,

26:53.680 --> 26:56.200
hoping to bring you both good luck.

26:57.320 --> 26:59.200
The embroidery
and inlaid designs on this one

26:59.280 --> 27:01.080
are exceptionally fine!

27:01.160 --> 27:02.360
This was stitched by Ming.

27:02.960 --> 27:04.600
Her needlework is more delicate.

27:05.480 --> 27:07.760
-And this was made by Zhao.
-Zhao…

27:11.760 --> 27:13.280
This tiger amulet is…

27:14.320 --> 27:15.280
Well, it's also a tiger amulet.

27:15.880 --> 27:17.320
It's, uh, nice.

27:17.400 --> 27:19.760
Please kindly accept them, gentlemen.

27:20.360 --> 27:21.800
Thank you, Madam.

27:23.040 --> 27:24.360
Thank you.

27:30.280 --> 27:32.760
Young Lady Zhao's embroidery is so clumsy,

27:32.840 --> 27:35.600
yet she clearly put in great effort
to make this tiger amulet for me.

27:36.120 --> 27:38.240
She loves me so much.

27:40.960 --> 27:42.520
Such a pity our personalities don't align,

27:42.600 --> 27:43.960
I'm bound to disappoint her.

27:44.720 --> 27:45.840
Young Lady Ming, on the other hand…

27:48.320 --> 27:50.720
Young Lady Zhao has
such a unique perspective

27:50.800 --> 27:51.760
and genuine sincerity.

27:51.840 --> 27:53.040
She's such a special girl.

27:59.160 --> 28:02.160
Gentlemen, the tea garden behind
our estate has beautiful scenery.

28:02.240 --> 28:04.720
Since it's your first visit here,

28:04.800 --> 28:07.960
I've arranged for a servant to
give you a tour there.

28:10.560 --> 28:11.760
Thank you, Madam.

28:15.080 --> 28:16.920
Since we both dislike the heat
and prefer peace,

28:17.000 --> 28:19.120
let's head to the pavilion instead.

28:19.200 --> 28:22.280
Once Zhao and Ming have
finished preparing the banquet,

28:22.360 --> 28:25.080
we can go straight there
for food and wine.

28:25.960 --> 28:27.280
-Shall we?
-Yes.

28:28.640 --> 28:29.840
After you.

28:41.400 --> 28:42.880
Everything is arranged.

28:42.960 --> 28:45.000
But that creature doesn't
understand human speech.

28:45.080 --> 28:47.480
How can we be sure it
will only attack the Marquis?

28:47.560 --> 28:48.840
What if it goes after
Young Master Wu instead?

28:48.920 --> 28:50.360
It won't make a mistake.

28:50.960 --> 28:52.800
It will definitely go for Wei Ting Yu.

28:53.320 --> 28:54.520
I've cleared the area of people.

28:54.600 --> 28:57.120
You must get Dou Zhao there on time.

28:57.640 --> 28:59.240
An hour later,

28:59.760 --> 29:02.520
I'll bring Lady Wei over.

29:03.240 --> 29:04.520
Yes, Madam.

29:10.520 --> 29:12.400
The scenery really is beautiful.

29:13.920 --> 29:15.280
It's all right, I suppose

29:27.760 --> 29:29.040
Young Master Wei.

29:31.720 --> 29:32.920
Thank you.

29:35.480 --> 29:36.800
Exquisite craftsmanship.

29:37.640 --> 29:39.600
Young Lady Ming has both skill and grace.

29:40.480 --> 29:41.800
Every bead on this amulet shows

29:41.880 --> 29:43.520
the care and effort she put into it.

29:44.480 --> 29:46.600
Young Lady Zhao put
her heart into hers as well.

29:46.680 --> 29:47.600
Her effort just carries…

29:48.920 --> 29:49.920
A more unique touch.

29:54.880 --> 29:57.080
A crane sings in the nine marshes,
and fish dwell deep in the abyss.

29:58.240 --> 29:59.320
But if reversed,

30:00.000 --> 30:01.600
the crane is no longer a crane,

30:01.680 --> 30:03.840
and the fish ceases to be a fish.

30:03.920 --> 30:05.680
If we were to exchange them,

30:05.760 --> 30:08.320
wouldn't that make everything perfect?

30:13.080 --> 30:14.600
But these are gifts
made by the young ladies,

30:14.680 --> 30:16.080
presented by the elders.

30:16.160 --> 30:17.360
To exchange them privately

30:18.160 --> 30:19.000
would be quite improper.

30:20.840 --> 30:22.760
Young Master Wu, I must disagree.

30:22.840 --> 30:25.280
Exchanging small festival gifts
is harmless fun.

30:25.800 --> 30:28.880
Besides, how could something
forced by elders bring true joy?

30:30.040 --> 30:31.000
Don't be mundane now.

30:33.760 --> 30:36.680
Young Master Wei,
this doesn't seem appropriate.

30:37.320 --> 30:38.320
Young Master Wei…

30:48.240 --> 30:51.480
Five dry dishes and five wet,
decent enough.

30:54.360 --> 30:56.200
The cold dishes shouldn't
be served in bowls,

30:56.280 --> 30:57.680
they need to be plated.

30:57.760 --> 30:58.760
Yes, Young Lady.

30:59.600 --> 31:04.200
Shred the duck meat before
serving the duck and barley soup.

31:04.880 --> 31:07.680
-Yes, Young Lady.
-Prepare more snowflake pastries.

31:07.760 --> 31:09.440
If there are any guests
who don't eat chilled foods,

31:09.520 --> 31:11.960
swap them out for room-temperature
mung bean pudding.

31:12.040 --> 31:13.360
Entertaining nobles

31:13.440 --> 31:14.800
requires such precision and attention.

31:15.400 --> 31:17.080
And you've thought of everything.

31:17.160 --> 31:20.040
But what about
the fruit serving dishes I picked?

31:20.120 --> 31:21.280
Did I choose the right ones?

31:24.840 --> 31:26.480
I'm so sorry, Young Lady Zhao!

31:27.640 --> 31:30.640
How clumsy! Thank goodness it wasn't hot.

31:30.720 --> 31:33.720
Come, Young Lady, let me help you
change in the side room.

31:33.800 --> 31:34.720
It's fine.

31:34.800 --> 31:36.320
I'll see to the banquet
arrangements first.

31:37.000 --> 31:38.480
There are so many guests today,

31:38.560 --> 31:39.800
and your clothing is so thin.

31:39.880 --> 31:42.480
If anyone sees you like this,
it could harm your reputation.

31:42.560 --> 31:44.240
You have to get changed right away.

31:45.960 --> 31:46.880
Zhao…

31:47.640 --> 31:49.040
Carry on with the preparation.
I'll go check on her.

31:50.720 --> 31:52.680
Your clothes are too thin,
you'll catch a cold!

31:53.280 --> 31:55.760
It'll be quick, just up ahead.
Come, hurry.

32:02.160 --> 32:03.960
MAGISTRATE OF THE OFFICE
OF STATE AFFAIRS, DAI JIAN

32:04.600 --> 32:05.880
This is just a modest gift
for the festival.

32:05.960 --> 32:07.880
Please accept it, My Lord.

32:15.880 --> 32:17.920
This is far from modest.

32:19.720 --> 32:20.840
You shouldn't have, Yuan Ji.

32:21.520 --> 32:23.800
Well, I shall accept it gratefully then.

32:25.480 --> 32:28.040
-Carry this to His Lordship's carriage.
-Yes, Master.

32:28.800 --> 32:30.160
-After you.
-Thank you.

32:30.240 --> 32:31.960
We're almost there.

32:32.040 --> 32:33.680
What's the rush, Nanny Zhou?

32:34.720 --> 32:36.800
The banquet is about to start.
There's no time to waste!

32:36.880 --> 32:38.760
I'll go with Zhao. I can shield her.

32:38.840 --> 32:40.400
No need, no need!

32:42.840 --> 32:46.680
What I mean is, I alone can
help her get changed.

32:46.760 --> 32:49.280
Why are you attacking me for no reason?

32:50.160 --> 32:51.800
We can take good care of Young Lady Zhao.

32:51.880 --> 32:53.040
What tricks are you trying to pull?

32:53.120 --> 32:56.640
-Nothing. I just want to help her…
-Yet you won't let Dou Ming follow.

32:56.720 --> 32:59.480
Now I'd really like to see
what's waiting for me in the room.

33:00.200 --> 33:03.040
HIDING TALENTS, WAITING TIME

33:10.080 --> 33:12.280
-Young Master Wu?
-How come it's Young Master Wu?

33:12.840 --> 33:14.280
While my master was strolling
in the back hills,

33:14.360 --> 33:16.520
a group of butterflies
suddenly swarmed him.

33:16.600 --> 33:17.880
He fainted shortly after.

33:19.800 --> 33:20.800
Butterflies?

33:35.760 --> 33:37.120
Quickly, call for a doctor

33:37.200 --> 33:38.040
and inform the elders.

33:39.160 --> 33:40.080
It's just a reaction
to the butterfly scales,

33:40.160 --> 33:41.760
causing some rashes and irritation.

33:41.840 --> 33:43.920
There's no need to disturb
the masters over this.

33:51.560 --> 33:54.200
The Miluo mourns unfulfilled regrets,

33:54.280 --> 33:56.080
yet bids the young to rest
in the southern hills.

33:57.680 --> 34:00.640
Qu Yuan perished in the Miluo River
during the Dragon Boat Festival.

34:00.720 --> 34:02.560
The poem hints at an untimely death.

34:09.760 --> 34:11.159
You're still trying to cover this up?

34:11.679 --> 34:13.560
Your plan was for a lone man
and an unmarried woman

34:14.080 --> 34:16.280
to be caught together while changing
clothes, forcing me into marriage.

34:16.360 --> 34:18.760
But you didn't expect that Wei Ting Yu
and Wu Shan would swap the amulets.

34:19.480 --> 34:22.639
For most people, these butterfly scales
only cause redness and itching,

34:22.719 --> 34:24.560
but Young Master Wu has a lung condition.

34:24.639 --> 34:25.560
This could kill him!

34:26.679 --> 34:28.639
Young Master Wu came
to our estate as a guest.

34:28.719 --> 34:30.199
If anything happens to him,

34:30.880 --> 34:32.480
how could we answer to the Wu family?

34:33.000 --> 34:34.080
Do as Zhao says immediately!

34:34.760 --> 34:35.679
Yes, Young Lady!

34:39.600 --> 34:40.719
His breathing is getting worse.

34:41.400 --> 34:43.880
The room is too stuffy
with all these drapes.

34:43.960 --> 34:45.000
Su Xin,

34:45.080 --> 34:46.800
get some men to carry him
to the courtyard,

34:46.880 --> 34:47.719
gently.

34:47.800 --> 34:49.440
And bring me my acupuncture kit.

34:49.520 --> 34:50.520
Yes, Young Lady!

34:58.760 --> 35:00.840
Our master is hosting guests.
No outsiders allowed.

35:05.240 --> 35:07.600
I am Song Mo, son of the Duke of Ying.

35:07.680 --> 35:11.120
I've come bearing gifts
for the Dragon Boat Festival!

35:15.040 --> 35:18.600
These days, Grand Secretary Wu's
words hold absolute sway at court.

35:18.680 --> 35:20.080
Who would dare oppose him?

35:20.720 --> 35:22.480
My words carry little weight.

35:22.560 --> 35:25.560
I'm powerless to aid His Majesty
in resolving his worries.

35:25.640 --> 35:27.480
The southeastern coast has
been ravaged by typhoons for miles.

35:29.080 --> 35:30.760
While others steer clear of disaster,

35:31.280 --> 35:33.880
the Dou family dares to walk
straight into the eye of the storm,

35:33.960 --> 35:35.320
seeking to ride the winds.

35:36.000 --> 35:37.440
Quite bold of them.

35:37.520 --> 35:39.600
Master, I tried to stop His Lordship.

35:42.920 --> 35:45.720
My family has no dealings
with the Duke of Ying's family.

35:46.320 --> 35:49.760
My Lord, to what do
we owe this uninvited visit?

35:53.120 --> 35:54.720
I heard you've been sending rice dumplings

35:54.800 --> 35:55.960
to every official in the capital.

35:56.640 --> 35:59.600
I was curious about the stuffing

36:00.520 --> 36:02.320
and asked Grand Secretary Wu
for a few to try.

36:11.880 --> 36:13.360
Turns out, it's gold.

36:15.000 --> 36:17.960
It seems Grand Secretary Wu holds
a rather deep prejudice against me.

36:18.040 --> 36:19.760
These were but ordinary festival gifts.

36:20.360 --> 36:23.080
If he feels they are excessive,
he could have declined politely,

36:23.160 --> 36:25.920
there was no need to trouble you
to deliver them back.

36:26.000 --> 36:28.040
My Lord, you'd better put the sword down.

36:28.120 --> 36:30.080
As the Magistrate of
the Office of State Affairs,

36:30.640 --> 36:33.040
I see this as a blatant threat
against a court official.

36:34.400 --> 36:35.680
I wouldn't dare.

36:39.800 --> 36:41.800
You…

36:42.760 --> 36:44.760
I've merely come to remind you

36:45.520 --> 36:48.480
that if you keep fabricating crimes
against the Duke of Ding,

36:49.160 --> 36:50.480
I'd have no choice

36:51.440 --> 36:52.720
but to present these dumplings
to His Majesty.

36:56.080 --> 36:59.520
By then, I doubt
even the Office of State Affairs

37:00.360 --> 37:02.000
could protect you.

37:02.600 --> 37:03.880
You…

37:05.880 --> 37:07.720
Master, Young Master Wu
has fallen unconscious.

37:07.800 --> 37:09.760
Young Lady Zhao has ordered
him to be carried to the courtyard.

37:09.840 --> 37:11.960
-Silence! Watch your tongue!
-Well, well.

37:12.560 --> 37:14.320
You even dared to harm
the Grand Secretary's grandson.

37:17.400 --> 37:19.880
Outrageous! Absolutely outrageous!

37:19.960 --> 37:22.120
This is your estate!

37:22.200 --> 37:26.520
I could not just let him walk away
after he disrespected you like that!

37:26.600 --> 37:27.600
Guards!

37:28.120 --> 37:30.280
Please don't, My Lord. My Lord!

37:30.360 --> 37:31.320
SPRING TREES AND EVENING CLOUDS

37:31.400 --> 37:34.680
My Lady, I understand you're worried
this marriage hasn't been settled yet.

37:34.760 --> 37:35.920
But in my opinion,

37:36.000 --> 37:38.760
once the spark of love ignites,

37:38.840 --> 37:41.400
nothing can stop it.

37:41.480 --> 37:43.280
-That's true.
-Ting Zhen!

37:46.920 --> 37:48.160
What are you doing here?

37:50.560 --> 37:53.720
Ting Zhen, Young Master Wu just…

37:59.520 --> 38:00.520
Song Mo?

38:14.760 --> 38:15.960
Su Xin, Su Lan.

38:17.040 --> 38:19.320
Young Lady Zhao, what are you doing?

38:27.960 --> 38:28.800
What are you doing to De Zhen?

38:33.480 --> 38:34.840
He's experiencing asphyxia
compounded by a lung abscess.

38:34.920 --> 38:36.080
His breathing is weakening.

38:36.160 --> 38:38.560
This means the infection
in his lungs has ruptured.

38:38.640 --> 38:40.800
It's practically a battle
with death at this point.

38:40.880 --> 38:43.800
I need to needle his Dazhui
and Xuanji points to save him.

38:47.000 --> 38:48.920
Dou Zhao! How dare you!

38:49.000 --> 38:52.720
You're taking off Young Master Wu's
clothes in broad daylight.

38:52.800 --> 38:54.600
What do you think you're doing? Get up!

38:54.680 --> 38:56.120
Mother, Young Master Wu suddenly fell ill.

38:56.200 --> 38:57.520
Zhao is trying to treat him
with acupuncture.

39:01.800 --> 39:04.240
This should be done by a proper doctor!

39:04.320 --> 39:05.960
There are boundaries
between men and women.

39:06.040 --> 39:08.200
You've disgraced yourself with
such an indecent act.

39:08.280 --> 39:09.240
If word of this gets out,

39:09.320 --> 39:11.320
what will people say about us?

39:11.400 --> 39:13.880
Someone, help Young Master Wu up!

39:13.960 --> 39:15.040
That's right.

39:18.080 --> 39:19.240
Mother, saving his life is more important!

39:19.320 --> 39:20.720
Shut up!

39:20.800 --> 39:23.640
Since it's asthma, he must be
taken to a doctor immediately.

39:23.720 --> 39:25.320
Take him to a doctor now!

39:25.400 --> 39:27.040
I've sent for a doctor,

39:27.720 --> 39:29.680
but the nearest clinic is ten miles away.

39:30.280 --> 39:32.480
By the time the doctor arrives,
Young Master Wu will be gone.

39:33.520 --> 39:34.560
My Lord, you grew up on the battlefield,

39:34.640 --> 39:36.960
so you know some injuries can't be moved

39:37.040 --> 39:38.280
and some emergencies can't wait.

39:48.240 --> 39:49.880
Please look me in the eyes.

39:50.880 --> 39:52.080
Since you can read people,

39:52.680 --> 39:54.000
you know I'm not lying.

39:54.520 --> 39:56.040
I can save him.

40:14.960 --> 40:16.280
Let go.

40:17.720 --> 40:18.560
Support De Zhen.

40:20.600 --> 40:22.960
Lu Zheng, bring all the screens
from the rooms

40:23.480 --> 40:25.520
-and set them up around them.
-Yes, My Lord.

40:27.800 --> 40:29.520
Everyone, turn around!

40:30.320 --> 40:31.600
If anyone dares to peek,

40:32.680 --> 40:34.680
they'll pay for it with their eyes.

40:44.680 --> 40:45.880
Young Lady Zhao,

40:46.720 --> 40:48.160
please administer the needles.

40:51.280 --> 40:52.280
My Lord,

40:53.120 --> 40:55.760
how dare you draw a blade
against a court official.

40:56.280 --> 40:57.480
Are you defying the imperial authority?

40:58.080 --> 41:00.240
I will kill whoever

41:01.160 --> 41:02.160
stands in my way today.

41:03.960 --> 41:05.520
You've repeatedly interfered
with efforts to save him.

41:05.600 --> 41:07.160
What's your motive?

41:08.000 --> 41:10.400
And what makes you believe that
this young woman can save him?

41:11.120 --> 41:12.480
I believe my judgment.

41:13.000 --> 41:15.200
-You…
-My Lord!

41:16.560 --> 41:19.200
You're causing such chaos on my estate.

41:19.280 --> 41:22.200
Do you really want to me to report
this matter directly to His Majesty?

41:23.400 --> 41:25.080
You know exactly

41:25.160 --> 41:27.680
why De Zhen fell ill, don't you?

41:28.480 --> 41:30.000
If this does reach His Majesty,

41:30.600 --> 41:33.120
let's see if your reputation and
the honor of your family's women

41:33.840 --> 41:36.320
survive the fallout.

41:41.000 --> 41:41.920
Mother.

41:47.440 --> 41:48.640
Mother!

41:49.160 --> 41:50.320
Dou Zhao,

41:50.400 --> 41:51.800
are you trying to get
the entire family killed?

41:52.400 --> 41:54.480
My Lord, what a scheme
you've set in motion.

41:55.160 --> 41:56.680
If anything happens to Young Master Wu,

41:56.760 --> 41:59.200
His Majesty will surely think
that our family

41:59.280 --> 42:01.840
is vying for power,
harming him out of political discord!

42:03.000 --> 42:04.280
Worry not, Yuan Ji.

42:05.000 --> 42:06.640
As the Magistrate of
the Office of State Affairs,

42:07.160 --> 42:09.280
I will attest to today's events.

42:09.880 --> 42:11.680
Song Mo stormed onto private property,

42:11.760 --> 42:13.320
brandished a weapon at court officials,

42:13.400 --> 42:14.840
and interfered with saving a life!

42:14.920 --> 42:17.600
Even if this reaches His Majesty,

42:17.680 --> 42:18.920
the facts remain as they are!

42:43.040 --> 42:44.960
The embroidery is quite unique.

42:45.040 --> 42:46.680
You're lucky that
Song Mo grew up in the military

42:46.760 --> 42:48.560
and doesn't understand the underhanded
schemes of the inner household.

42:48.640 --> 42:50.760
Otherwise, today could have
spelled disaster for the entire family!

42:50.840 --> 42:52.160
Watch your tongue!

42:52.240 --> 42:53.800
She risked her reputation to save you.
It was genuine.

42:53.880 --> 42:56.600
Are you suggesting Young Lady Zhao
has feelings for me too?

44:48.520 --> 44:50.880
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA
ARE FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
